*BLUF:* Are we able to provide ~ 30 Soldiers to support the TNMAN Exercise
(SECFOR ~ 20 Pax, UAS - 4 Pax, ICP Support ~ x# Pax, Comms Support ~ x#
Pax)?

All Concerned see attached TNMAN - 26 WG .pptx slides.

It seems that the estimate of our involvement has increased from 2 Pax for
a security task to ~ 30 Pax for multiple tasks within 7 days.

The immediate urgent question before us is, between the three Battalions,
can we assemble at least a 30 Pax Task Force to support the
overarching TNMAN-26 Exercise?

13 MAY - ADVON
14 MAY - Main Body
15 MAY - (ENDEX) ExFil

I will soon be in communication with the TNNG Planner for this exercise and
will push forward as much detail as I am given. Please collect your
questions and record them. I will collect them after I have more detailed
data.

Please respond as soon as possible with your BN's ability to support this
exercise with the number of Soldiers available.

-- 
V/R

JOHN T. SHEAF
LTC, TNSG
S3, 3 RGT
717.673.6177
john.sheaf@tnstateguard.org

